   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VrS86.1 (mss. 2005, 2010, 2030, 2040, 2101, 2102, 2104, 2106, 2109, 5020):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            barišn zōt ud rāspīg harw dō bē gōwišn <em>vīspaēibiiō sastīm baraiti ātarš mazdā̊ ahurahe</em></ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "Here, he should take the <em>barsom</em> from the <em>māhrōy</em>, be standing and bring homage to the fire. Both, <em>zōt</em> and <em>rāspīg</em>, have to recite
            <em>vīspaēibiiō sastīm baraiti ātarš mazdā̊ ahurahe</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
      <Commentary id="ritualCommentary">In the lesser performances, the same ritual action is carried out at Y62.1.
      </Commentary>
   </Ritual>
